<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Spreganje">Spreganje</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Sloven%C5%A1%C4%8Dina&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=9" title="Uredi razdelek: Spreganje" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Sloven%C5%A1%C4%8Dina&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Spreganje"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
